About me
I'm always up for a bit of banter so you can shout at me by PM or highlight and I'll even go as far as to step out of Nandos to shut that gob of yours. I mainly hang out in #osumania and occasionally tune in to #english.

I'm also a petrolhead and an Initial D & JDM fanboy


Peripherals/Settings
Peripherals
Keyboards: CM Storm Quickfire TK (Cherry MX red/brown) / Razer Blackwidow Ultimate 2013 Expert (Cherry MX blue)
Mouse: Razer Abyssus @ 450dpi (6/11 sens. in windows, 2.14x in osu)
Monitor: BenQ XL2411T 24", 144Hz, 1920x1080
Mousepad: Razer Goliathus Control(44x35cm)
Wrist rest: Matting soft gel wrist rest
I have a Wacom bamboo pen CTL-470 tablet, but I only use it to play with relax mod sometimes. I use full area for it

Settings
Standard clicks: B N

Mania layout
4K: Z X . / Preferred mode
5K: Z X , . /

7K: Q W E SPACE K L ;
8K: TAB Q W E SPACE K L ;

Scroll speed: 24 (Fixed)
Setup

CPU: Intel i5 2500K @ 4.5GHz
CPU cooler: Corsair H80
RAM: 4x4GB Corsair Vengeance
GPU: Gainward GTX970 4GB w/ Corsair HG10 N970 waterblock & H100i loop
PSU: Corsair RM850x
HDDS: 128GB Corsair Force LX as boot drive and some storage drives
